<br>
<!--EZCODE IMAGE START--><img src="http://www.firstnethou.com/dcd/cabilis/bones.jpg"><!--EZCODE IMAGE END--><br>
<br>
(Don't worry, the skeletons in Kurn's don't actually aggro in such huge numbers, unless you get impatient like me and run everywhere on the floor annoying them all before training them to one spot to be finished off at once.)<br>
<br>
And just for the heck of it, here are a couple of nice snapshots of Divine Might in action against a Kurn's skeleton (taken a few seconds apart):<br>
